        </item>
        <item>
            <title>FUJIFILM 宣佈菲林大幅加價，最高加價達 52%</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/05/fujifilm-price-hike/dc/photogism/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=fujifilm-price-hike</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/05/fujifilm-price-hike/dc/photogism/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 05 Apr 2025 13:00:48 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[攝影文化]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[fujifilm]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[菲林]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1301765</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>菲林攝影雖然近年迎來懷舊復興潮，不過菲林價格就一直上漲。最近 FUJIFILM 又再宣佈，部分攝影菲林產品在日本市場將進行價格調整，最大加價幅度更達到 52%。<br /><span id="more-1301765"></span></p><p>根據公告，彩色負片菲林（135）價格將上漲約 21 至 22％，正片菲林（135／120）則將上漲約 31 至 52％。他們表示上調價格原因為「難以應對零件、原材料價格及運輸成本的大幅上漲」，但尚未公佈具體受加價影響的產品型號。</p><p>此外，即用即棄相機「寫ルンです」的外包裝將從目前的袋裝改為紙盒型式。隨著包裝變更，外包裝設計和機身標籤設計也將全面更新。產品本身規格維持不變，但就會加價 44%。新規格產品預計於 2025 年 4 月開始出貨。</p><figure id="attachment_1301772" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1301772" style="width: 694px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot20250405at-694x283.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="283" class="size-medium wp-image-1301772" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot20250405at-694x283.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot20250405at.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1301772" class="wp-caption-text">Screenshot</figcaption></figure><p>FUJIFILM 在致客戶的公告中表示，儘管他們透過提高生產效率和削減費用等方式努力吸收成本，但在零件、原材料價格和運輸成本持續攀升的情況下，僅靠企業努力已難以應對，因此不得不對部分菲林產品進行價格調整。FUJIFILM 希望客戶理解此一情況，並感謝客戶一直以來對 FUJIFILM 產品的支持。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.fujifilm.com/ffis/ja/news/177">FUJIFILM</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/05/fujifilm-price-hike/dc/photogism/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Microsoft 升級 Copilot AI 助理，加入更多實用互動功能</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/05/microsoft-50-copilot/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=microsoft-50-copilot</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/05/microsoft-50-copilot/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 05 Apr 2025 12:00:02 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Copilot]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[office]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1301754</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Microsoft AI 總裁 Mustafa Suleyman 近日宣佈，將推出一系列 Copilot 更新，旨在將其塑造成真正個人化的 AI 助理。Suleyman 表示：「當我回顧 Microsoft 50 年來持續創新所帶來的巨大影響，我受到 Bill Gates 多年前大膽願景的啟發：讓每張桌面和每個家庭都有一台電腦。如今，我們正在創造 Copilot，一個屬於每個人的 AI 伴侶。」<br /><span id="more-1301754"></span></p><p>全新 Copilot 將會加入「記憶」功能，經用戶許可後，它將記住你討論的內容，學習你的喜好、生活細節，如寵物名字、工作項目或健身計劃等。它能在適當的時機以適當的方式理解並融入你的生活環境。Suleyman 強調：「這種關係比我們之前見過的任何軟件都更豐富、更動態、更支持且更具潛力，是與技術關係的全新型態。」</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_38958"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/H54C6MVyk5U?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>此外新版本還會加入類似以前 Office「小幫手」般的形象，讓用家在互動時有更加親切的使用體驗，也可以自訂不同的外觀配合興趣。經典 Office 小幫手「萬字夾」也會是其中一個選項。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_92798"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/HhP1Hn9Z9PM?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>除了核心功能，Microsoft 還推出多項創新服務。例如「行動」功能允許 Copilot 代表用戶執行任務，如預訂活動門票、餐廳或送禮物。「視覺」功能則擴展至手機和 Windows 平台，讓用戶能與現實世界進行實時互動。「頁面」功能幫助整理思緒和內容，「播客」功能可基於用戶興趣生成個人化音頻內容。「購物」功能則充當個人購物助理，「深度研究」能高效執行複雜的多步驟研究任務。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_38557"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/aisTyhgZcUI?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_50675"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/v3_BJiI0vvA?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_23955"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/X7_02PXumHE?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>儘管提供如此多樣化的功能，Suleyman 強調：「Copilot 不僅是一個 AI，它是屬於你的。它記住的不只是你説過的話，還有你是誰。而你始終保持控制權，你是駕駛員，你做決定並設定界限。」Microsoft 已開始推出這些新體驗，並將在未來數週和數月內繼續擴大其可用性。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://blogs.microsoft.com/blog/2025/04/04/your-ai-companion/">Microsoft</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/05/microsoft-50-copilot/ai/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
