        </item>
        <item>
            <title>美國網紅 IShowSpeed 深圳看中國科技，狂買華為 Mate XT 三摺機、叫無人機外賣、比亞迪 U8 落水</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/05/ishowspeed/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ishowspeed</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/05/ishowspeed/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 05 Apr 2025 09:45:34 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ishowspeed]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1301783</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>美國網紅 IShowSpeed（甲亢哥）於 4 月 5 日抵達深圳，展開了他的中國之行。他首度體驗了比亞迪仰望 U8 這款能在水中行駛的豪華吉普車，並與粉絲一同分享了驚險刺激的經歷。他也在深圳的華為旗艦店瘋狂購物，當場買下三部華為 Mate XT 摺疊手機，並即刻開箱展示。</p><p>在直播的開場，「甲亢哥」的首個挑戰是乘坐比亞迪的仰望 U8。上車前，他表現出一些不安，擔心車輛會沉入水中，並詢問助手是否確保他會安全。助手則提議不綁安全帶，認為這樣他能更快脫困。但當車子實際駛入水中時，「甲亢哥」的情緒顯得非常緊張不斷尖叫，他一度擔心車子會沈下去，並且焦急地要求司機把車開回岸邊。在成功回到沙灘後，「甲亢哥」原本打算自己試駕這輛車，但由於沙地過軟，車輛無法前進。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301785" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301784" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>隨後，他來到位於深圳的萬象天地華為旗艦店，並對店內展示的三摺疊手機 Mate XT 表現出極大興趣。他對手機的設計讚不絕口，當場購買了三部 Mate XT，並在車上立刻開箱，不停地驚呼「這款手機太瘋狂了！」。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-5.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301789" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-5-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-5-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-5.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-6.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301790" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-6-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-6-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-6.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>在隨後的直播中，「甲亢哥」不僅與粉絲互動，還帶著粉絲遊覽深圳的人才公園，並體驗了美團的無人機外賣服務。當他看到無人機送來他點的 KFC 時，他大為驚喜。他還用手機直播了無人機配送的過程，並向粉絲介紹了中國在科技和物流領域的創新。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301786" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301787" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-4.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301788" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>資料來源：IShowSpeed</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
